description: Don’t be surprised if this vegie-packed noodle stir-fry becomes a weeknight dinner go-to. It’s ready in 15 minutes and requires only five ingredients.
keywords: Stir-fry,Pescatarian,Quick & easy dinner,High fibre,High protein,Seafood free,Low sugar,Sesame free,Dairy free
name: Super Quick Veggie Noodle Stir Fry Recipe | Woolworths
recipeIngredient: 1 Simply Cook Layered Stir Fry Kit with Honey Soy Sauce

recipeInstructions.text: Heat 2 tsp oil in a large frying pan over a high heat. Add stirfry vegetable mix, leaving sauce to the side, and cook for 3 minutes.
Meanwhile, soak noodles in a medium sized bowl for 3 minutes in boiling water, then break apart gently with a fork and drain.
Add noodles and honey soy sauce (from the kit) to frying pan with the vegetables and cook for a further 2 minutes, stirring frequently.

In a separate nonstick frying pan, heat remaining oil over medium heat and fry eggs, sunny-side up, or to your liking. Stir cashews through stir fry, divide among four bowls and top each with an egg to serve.
